info.value:
Returns detailed information on a Champion, including description, stats, image ex: 
 ` >info Aatrox `

summon.value:
Returns information on a Summoner like they're level, rank, player icon ex: 
 `>summon KR Faker`

runes.value:
Returns an image of the highest win-rate Runes on that champion ex: 
 ` >runes Aatrox `

build.value:
Returns an image of the highest win-rate Build on that champion ex: 
 ` >build Aatrox `

skills.value:
Returns an image of the highest win-rate Skill order on that champion ex: 
 ` >skills Aatrox `

stats.value:
Returns an image of all the stats for that champion ex: 
 ` >stats Aatrox `

sums.value:
Returns an image of the highest win-rate Summoner Spells on that champion ex: 
 ` >sums Aatrox `

matchups.value:
Returns an image of the best and worst matchups on that champion ex: 
 ` >matchups Aatrox `
